<p><a href="http://www.scifi.com/battlestar/video/index.php?clip=17&amp;sub=blog" title="http://www.scifi.com/battlestar/video/index.php?clip=17&amp;sub=blog">http://www.scifi.com/battlestar/video/index.php?clip=17&amp;sub=blog</a></p>
